title: Sahithi Chindam
text:
Sahithi Chindam is currently pursuing Masters degree in Advanced Data Analytics at the University of North Texas. she completed her undergraduation in Electronics and Communication Engineering from JNTU Hyderabad. Following the completion of her bachelorâ€™s degree. She worked for 2.7 years as a Data Analyst in Accenture. During this period, her primary emphasis was on Business Intelligence, where she worked on QlikSense and Tableau for data analysis. Currently, she is also engaged in part-time employment as a desk clerk at a UNT residence hall. This role has allowed her to enhance interpersonal abilities and gain valuable insights into customer service.
In three words, she would describe herself as analytical, inquisitive, and data-driven. She is passionate about the world of data analytics.
Proficient in QlikSense, QlikView, Tableau, PowerBI, RStudio, Python, Postgresql, Web Analytics, Matomo, and Microsoft Office.
